<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_248_r2l1">Wır ~ dıe <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc / Bekennen etc / Als der <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleẅchtıgıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l2">fürſt vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Sıgmu<ex>n</ex>d</expan> <expan>Römıſch<ex>er</ex></expan> künıg cʒu <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ʒeıten merer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l3">des Reıchs vnd ʒu <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu Beheım dalmacıen Croacıen etc kunıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> des <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> Reıchs <expan>kurfürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>fürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l5">grafen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vnd Stette . auf den ſunntag Jubılate drey <expan>woche<ex>n</ex></expan> nach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l6"><expan>Oſt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſchıerıſtkünftıg / Von <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>notdürftıg<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l7"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd verbodt hat ʒu Jm gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . Vnd dıe <expan>hochwırdıg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l8">vnd <expan>hochgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>fürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> ʒu Meıncʒ <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Ott ʒu tryer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l9"><expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> dıetreıch ʒu . Cöln Ercʒbıſchöffe Vnd <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>lud<ex>wig</ex></expan> pfallncʒgraf bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l10">Reyn vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> in Peyern etc . des <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Römiſche<ex>n</ex></expan> Reıchs <expan>kurfürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l11"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> gnedıg <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündt</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ ſıe auf den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l12"><expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> tag gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> auch ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd darauf an vns ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l13"><expan>ſunne<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Jn vnd den Jren geleyt ʒu <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſo geben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l14">wır den <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ den <expan>kurfurſte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Otten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l15">vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıetr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Ercʒbıſchoff<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan> <expan>Pfallncʒgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> etc . Jren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l16">grafen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Reten <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>knecht<ex>en</ex></expan> dıenern vnd den <expan>Jre<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd nemlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l17"><expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den dıe ſıe mıt Jn auf dıe <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ʒeıt gen . <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>brınge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l18">bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> auf dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> tag vnd weıl <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> tag vnd teydıng </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l19">weren ein ſlecht geleyt on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . Mıt <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dıcʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> . <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıgelt</expan> mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r2l20"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> ʒu ruck <expan>aufgedrukte<ex>n</ex></expan> Jnſıgel <expan>Geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_248" id="123r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
