<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc., bekennen etc., als der
              <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> durchlewchtigist fürst und
            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Sigmu<ex>n</ex>d</expan>
<expan>römisch<ex>er</ex></expan> künig, czu <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> zeiten merer
            des reichs und zu <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, zu Beheim, Dalmacien, Croacien etc.,
            kunig, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, des <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> reichs <expan>kurfürste<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                <expan>fürste<ex>n</ex></expan>, grafen, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, und stette <app>
<note><q type="date">auf den sunntag jubilate drey wochen nach
                    <expan>ost<ex>er</ex>n</expan> schieristkünftig</q>13.04.1421</note>
</app> von <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> und
              <expan>notdürftig<ex>er</ex></expan> sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und verbodt hat, zu im gen
              <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> zu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, und die
                <expan>hochwirdig<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>hochgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fürste<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
              <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> zu Meincz, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Ott zu Tryer,
                <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Dietreich zu Cöln, erczbischöffe, und
              <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan> pfallnczgraf bey Reyn und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
            in Peyern etc., des <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> reichs <expan>kurfürste<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> gnedig <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, uns
                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündt</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sie auf den <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> tag
            gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> auch zu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan> und darauf an uns <expan>gesunne<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, in und den iren geleyt zu <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
            also geben wir den <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, den <expan>kurfurste<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Otten und
                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Dietr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>erczbischoff<ex>en</ex></expan>, und
                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan>
<expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. iren grafen, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
            reten, <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>knecht<ex>en</ex></expan>, dienern und
            den <expan>ire<ex>n</ex></expan> und nemlich <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den, die sie
            mit in auf die <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> zeit gen
              <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>bringe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, bey uns zu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> auf dem
                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> tag und weil <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> tag
            und teyding weren ein slecht geleyt on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Mit
                <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sigelt</expan> mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> zu ruck
                <expan>aufgedrukte<ex>n</ex></expan> insigel <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ut
                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
